WEBVTT

01:51.580 --> 01:52.220
I'm heading back.

01:53.380 --> 01:53.940
Lawyer Xu,

01:58.300 --> 01:59.580
the rain was pouring yesterday,

01:59.979 --> 02:00.860
and I got out of the car in a hurry.

02:01.580 --> 02:02.979
I didn't get a chance to thank you.

02:04.819 --> 02:05.860
Thank you for driving me back.

02:07.660 --> 02:08.339
It was on my way.

02:09.740 --> 02:10.339
Wait a minute.

02:18.299 --> 02:18.859
I'm ready.

02:19.180 --> 02:20.220
Alright, alright.

02:20.220 --> 02:20.900
I'm coming.

02:41.660 --> 02:42.419
This is for you.

02:45.460 --> 02:46.579
How to say goodbye properly?

02:53.699 --> 02:55.139
Actually, he has helped me

02:56.539 --> 02:57.220
beyond

02:57.220 --> 02:58.380
the obligation of a lawyer.

03:01.180 --> 03:02.579
After the last meeting tomorrow,

03:04.259 --> 03:05.620
I'll give him a gift.

03:06.819 --> 03:08.299
Ruan Yu at 28

03:08.699 --> 03:10.139
gives a gift

03:10.620 --> 03:11.380
to Ruan Yu at 18

03:11.380 --> 03:12.460
who didn't have the chance to give it.

03:13.579 --> 03:16.180
This ending is considered satisfactory, right?

03:19.340 --> 03:20.460
The court trial tomorrow

03:21.259 --> 03:23.139
Lawyer Liu will be present.

03:24.699 --> 03:25.419
After today,

03:26.180 --> 03:28.259
I may not see you anymore.

03:29.460 --> 03:31.180
After all, you are usually

03:31.460 --> 03:32.259
quite busy.

03:34.299 --> 03:35.859
Thank you for your help

03:36.819 --> 03:37.500
during this time.

03:39.380 --> 03:40.660
Although Lawyer Liu said

03:41.180 --> 03:42.819
you don't need to pay me,

03:45.180 --> 03:46.019
I still want to

03:48.019 --> 03:50.060
express my gratitude.

03:54.859 --> 03:55.660
This is for you.

04:11.900 --> 04:12.579
For you.

04:19.500 --> 04:20.819
I hope that

04:23.500 --> 04:25.820
your life and career

04:26.780 --> 04:27.939
will go well

04:30.379 --> 04:31.460
in the future.

04:58.340 --> 04:58.820
Thank you.

05:15.619 --> 05:16.979
Who said we won't meet again?

05:26.220 --> 05:28.780
I'll be there for tomorrow's trial.

06:05.539 --> 06:06.660
What does she mean?

06:06.900 --> 06:08.220
What do you mean?

06:08.379 --> 06:09.140
I want to know

06:09.140 --> 06:10.499
what you mean.

06:27.820 --> 06:30.100
First, she said we wouldn't meet again,

06:31.619 --> 06:33.059
then she gave you a digital watch.

06:34.539 --> 06:35.379
What does that mean?

06:37.979 --> 06:39.220
The past is not worth lingering over.

06:39.580 --> 06:40.979
Time will wash away everything.

06:43.460 --> 06:44.619
Is it possible

06:44.619 --> 06:46.700
that it means something else?

06:47.260 --> 06:50.820
When Ruan Yu said there was no chance to meet again,

06:51.660 --> 06:53.580
she wanted you to take the initiative

06:53.580 --> 06:55.700
to create more opportunities to meet.

06:56.900 --> 07:00.299
And the digital watch

07:01.780 --> 07:02.979
was to express

07:02.979 --> 07:04.979
he cherishes the time

07:04.979 --> 07:06.020
he spent with you.

07:11.820 --> 07:12.979
Think about it.

07:13.820 --> 07:15.859
Why did he give you an electronic watch

07:16.220 --> 07:17.580
instead of a mechanical one?

07:18.499 --> 07:19.619
What does Ruan Yu do?

07:20.379 --> 07:21.539
He's a writer,

07:21.739 --> 07:22.780
playing with words.

07:24.340 --> 07:26.900
There must be a meaning behind it.

07:29.739 --> 07:30.419
Think about it.

07:32.580 --> 07:33.179
Think about it.

07:33.820 --> 07:35.220
What does "electric" mean?

07:36.419 --> 07:37.979
It sounds like "miss".

07:38.660 --> 07:39.340
Zi.

07:41.220 --> 07:42.379
It means days.

07:42.700 --> 07:43.859
Days, right?

07:45.059 --> 07:45.820
Biao.

07:48.179 --> 07:48.939
Biao.

07:51.900 --> 07:54.419
Biao.

07:58.059 --> 07:58.900
If you read "Biyao" fast,

07:58.900 --> 07:59.660
it sounds like "Biao".

08:01.619 --> 08:02.900
Biyao.

08:03.580 --> 08:04.939
Right? What does it mean?

08:05.939 --> 08:07.580
It means that

08:07.580 --> 08:08.859
with Ruan Yu,

08:09.700 --> 08:10.299
were the days

08:10.299 --> 08:11.580
she had to remember.

08:12.059 --> 08:14.660
She's been keeping it in mind.

08:16.020 --> 08:16.900
I finally made it.

08:17.260 --> 08:18.859
If Ruan Yu plays with words like this,

08:18.859 --> 08:20.299
she would have long left the writer circle.

08:23.059 --> 08:23.580
In short,

08:23.580 --> 08:24.220
in a word,

08:24.220 --> 08:25.379
don't worry about what the watch

08:25.379 --> 08:25.939
means.

08:25.939 --> 08:26.820
It's just a gift

08:27.460 --> 08:28.539
is just a gesture.

08:28.539 --> 08:29.059
Right?

08:29.220 --> 08:30.539
If you really can't figure it out,

08:30.539 --> 08:31.340
don't just sit here

08:31.340 --> 08:31.859
overthinking it.

08:31.859 --> 08:32.580
Just ask her.

08:32.580 --> 08:33.379
That's all there is to it.

08:40.340 --> 08:40.979
Bro,

08:42.460 --> 08:43.259
when it comes to court battles,

08:44.259 --> 08:45.580
I can't beat you.

08:46.460 --> 08:48.019
But in the realm of relationships,

08:49.659 --> 08:50.739
I'm a veteran.

08:51.619 --> 08:53.019
in this field.

08:57.979 --> 08:58.619
Didn't you see

08:58.619 --> 08:59.580
my WeChat Moments yesterday?

09:00.499 --> 09:01.460
My blind date

09:02.019 --> 09:02.940
was successful.

09:03.779 --> 09:04.580
We fell in love

09:05.060 --> 09:06.859
at first sight,

09:06.859 --> 09:08.220
and we are very happy.

09:08.540 --> 09:09.580
We will have a big family.

09:12.659 --> 09:14.060
If everything goes well,

09:14.060 --> 09:14.619
we will...

09:22.420 --> 09:22.940
Shanshan,

09:25.420 --> 09:26.100
I'm not busy.

09:26.739 --> 09:27.619
Okay, okay.

09:28.580 --> 09:29.259
The same restaurant

09:29.259 --> 09:30.460
you booked last time, right?

09:30.779 --> 09:31.739
Okay, no problem.

09:32.779 --> 09:34.019
Okay, okay.

09:34.779 --> 09:35.259
See you later.

09:35.700 --> 09:36.619
Okay, bye.

09:38.499 --> 09:38.979
I have to go.

09:38.979 --> 09:39.659
I have something important to do.

09:39.899 --> 09:40.580
I can't accompany you anymore.

09:44.379 --> 09:45.739
If you don't believe what I said,

09:48.499 --> 09:49.180
then don't

09:49.180 --> 09:49.899
sneak around

09:49.899 --> 09:50.779
and ask her yourself.

09:51.540 --> 09:52.420
Stubborn.

09:54.820 --> 09:56.100
You think I'm like you,

09:56.340 --> 09:57.499
so impatient?

11:17.259 --> 11:18.100
Lawyer Xu,

11:18.540 --> 11:19.220
why are you here?

11:20.540 --> 11:21.220
I'll take you home.

11:34.019 --> 11:34.979
Why is the weather

11:35.379 --> 11:36.700
always so miserable?

11:38.220 --> 11:39.820
[This sudden downpour]

11:40.060 --> 11:41.700
[is like an unexpected farewell,]

11:42.180 --> 11:43.659
[seemingly without any warning,]

11:44.259 --> 11:46.060
[but the seeds of sorrow]

11:46.420 --> 11:47.700
[have long been sown]

11:48.019 --> 11:49.859
[in the desolate air.]

11:54.499 --> 11:55.300
Why does the radio

11:55.700 --> 11:57.019
always have ill intentions?

12:10.899 --> 12:12.220
Why would you give me this?

12:16.499 --> 12:17.619
I heard from Lawyer Liu

12:18.259 --> 12:19.659
that you often

12:19.659 --> 12:20.580
stay up late when busy.

12:21.139 --> 12:21.979
I thought

12:22.259 --> 12:23.899
an electronic watch can monitor

12:23.899 --> 12:25.540
your blood pressure, heart rate

12:25.540 --> 12:26.340
and other health data,

12:27.019 --> 12:28.619
so that it can remind you

12:28.739 --> 12:29.820
to take care of yourself.

12:30.820 --> 12:31.700
Don't be in a hurry.

12:32.019 --> 12:32.940
Wait and see.

12:33.340 --> 12:35.420
Let's see if she will send you candies

12:35.700 --> 12:36.899
when you are not busy.

12:40.619 --> 12:42.139
What's your intention?

12:46.139 --> 12:47.019
According to the professional ethics,

12:47.340 --> 12:48.220
a lawyer can't accept

12:48.220 --> 12:49.060
from clients.

12:49.859 --> 12:50.420
If you're

12:50.420 --> 12:51.220
giving this to me

12:51.220 --> 12:52.220
as a client,

12:52.820 --> 12:53.619
I need to return it.

12:55.460 --> 12:56.060
No, no.

12:56.700 --> 12:58.100
You haven't even charged me,

12:58.739 --> 12:59.979
so technically,

13:00.460 --> 13:01.979
you're not my lawyer yet.

13:02.700 --> 13:03.420
Of course,

13:03.420 --> 13:04.460
it's not from a client.

13:05.300 --> 13:05.820
Then...

13:09.979 --> 13:10.659
Lawyer Xu,

13:11.619 --> 13:12.379
we can be

13:13.060 --> 13:14.100
considered as friends, right?

13:17.139 --> 13:17.659
Of course.

13:53.220 --> 13:53.859
Hello, babe.

13:54.779 --> 13:55.540
Hello, Chuan.

13:55.820 --> 13:57.100
Why did it take so long to answer?

13:57.340 --> 13:58.259
Are you still at the company?

13:59.100 --> 14:00.340
I was just busy.

14:01.420 --> 14:01.859
Is your company

14:01.859 --> 14:03.060
humane at all?

14:03.139 --> 14:04.300
They're just picking on you.

14:05.820 --> 14:06.979
I have no choice.

14:07.220 --> 14:08.340
I have to do live streaming

14:08.340 --> 14:09.379
and product selection myself.

14:09.899 --> 14:11.259
And I have to attend some social events.

14:12.060 --> 14:12.619
I'm almost

14:12.619 --> 14:13.659
a time management expert.

14:15.779 --> 14:16.779
It's late.

14:16.779 --> 14:18.100
You have to eat.

14:18.259 --> 14:18.899
I'll go right now.

14:19.019 --> 14:19.940
I'll eat later.

14:20.300 --> 14:20.820
I'll hang up now.

14:20.820 --> 14:21.540
I have to go.

14:26.100 --> 14:27.300
Someone is waiting for you to eat.

14:29.180 --> 14:30.300
My mom.

14:31.100 --> 14:32.019
She's always afraid that I'm too busy

14:32.019 --> 14:32.820
to eat.

14:34.180 --> 14:34.859
Let's go.

14:37.060 --> 14:39.220
Eat. Don't let your mom worry.

15:29.460 --> 15:30.940
Aren't you afraid of being seen?

15:34.619 --> 15:35.899
So what if they see?

16:07.220 --> 16:08.139
Baby, why are you here?

16:08.659 --> 16:09.659
I'm about to go to a meeting.

16:10.180 --> 16:11.460
I saw you hadn't replied to my messages,

16:11.460 --> 16:12.259
so I came up directly.

16:12.899 --> 16:13.420
Here.

16:14.220 --> 16:15.460
I've been too busy today

16:15.460 --> 16:16.420
to check my phone.

16:16.739 --> 16:17.820
I have a meeting to attend.

16:18.100 --> 16:19.139
I can't be with you today.

16:22.619 --> 16:23.019
By the way,

16:23.420 --> 16:24.739
did you park the car downstairs?

16:25.220 --> 16:26.300
You can't park there.

16:26.300 --> 16:27.300
You'll get a parking ticket.

16:27.540 --> 16:28.619
You need to move it quickly.

16:29.180 --> 16:29.899
One minute.

16:30.899 --> 16:32.259
I have no choice.

16:33.180 --> 16:33.899
Fine.

16:33.899 --> 16:35.180
I can't stay with you today.

16:35.820 --> 16:36.619
I'll go first.

16:38.779 --> 16:39.420
I'll go home with you.

16:41.340 --> 16:41.820
Fine.

16:56.979 --> 16:57.659
Who is that?

17:00.700 --> 17:01.619
A delivery guy.

17:02.220 --> 17:02.779
No one took the order,

17:02.779 --> 17:03.859
so the merchant delivered it himself.

17:05.659 --> 17:07.019
You said you were going back to the office to get something.

17:07.379 --> 17:08.379
Is it to get takeout?

17:09.019 --> 17:09.859
Are you that hungry?

17:13.419 --> 17:14.100
What do you think?

17:21.260 --> 17:22.139
Thank you, Lawyer Xu.

17:22.859 --> 17:24.219
Drive slowly on your way back.

17:36.300 --> 17:38.500
Lawyer Xu, do you have a stomachache?

17:41.659 --> 17:42.219
It's okay.

17:43.980 --> 17:44.820
I've been tired all day,

17:45.419 --> 17:46.300
and I haven't had the chance to eat.

17:46.459 --> 17:47.939
I must be hungry, it's fine.

17:50.179 --> 17:50.939
Why don't you

17:52.619 --> 17:53.619
come up and eat something?

18:07.980 --> 18:08.540
Come in.

18:13.419 --> 18:14.100
Lawyer Xu,

18:15.619 --> 18:16.419
You can wear this.

18:17.419 --> 18:18.139
It's new.

18:19.179 --> 18:20.699
I bought it last time

18:20.780 --> 18:22.300
when you visited my home.

18:23.100 --> 18:23.740
Thank you.

18:31.100 --> 18:32.540
You should change your clothes.

18:35.219 --> 18:35.740
OK.

18:36.980 --> 18:38.300
Please wait a minute.

18:39.300 --> 18:39.859
OK.

19:24.899 --> 19:26.379
I bought it last time

19:26.500 --> 19:28.020
when you visited my home.

19:29.340 --> 19:31.100
Who visited my home?

19:51.419 --> 19:53.020
[He shouldn't have heard that.]

21:25.859 --> 21:26.859
Lawyer Xu, are you okay?

21:30.139 --> 21:30.619
I'm fine.

21:34.619 --> 21:35.459
Let me see.

21:35.459 --> 21:37.020
It's okay. I can do it myself.

21:39.580 --> 21:40.260
Are you okay?

21:41.699 --> 21:42.219
I'm fine.

21:43.619 --> 21:44.580
The windows are closed.

21:44.580 --> 21:45.580
It might be a bit stuffy.

21:46.540 --> 21:47.060
I'll open them.

21:51.260 --> 21:52.060
Maybe it's over there.

21:54.980 --> 21:55.500
It's open.

21:56.179 --> 21:56.740
Yeah.

21:58.459 --> 21:59.459
I didn't sleep well

22:00.260 --> 22:01.300
last night.

22:01.699 --> 22:02.459
I'm a little dizzy.

22:03.340 --> 22:04.139
I'll take a break.

22:04.740 --> 22:05.459
Lawyer Xu,

22:05.619 --> 22:06.820
take a break.

22:06.820 --> 22:07.780
I'll cook for you.

22:08.179 --> 22:09.260
Thank you.

22:10.659 --> 22:11.699
What do you want to eat?

22:13.100 --> 22:14.500
Anything simple is fine.

22:14.820 --> 22:15.340
I'll cook

22:15.340 --> 22:16.459
some easy-to-digest noodles.

22:16.540 --> 22:17.020
Okay.

22:18.300 --> 22:19.139
Let me help you.

22:19.939 --> 22:20.740
No, no need.

22:21.179 --> 22:23.379
It only takes me five minutes to cook noodles.

22:25.540 --> 22:26.980
You should rest.

22:28.340 --> 22:28.820
Okay.

22:56.179 --> 22:57.340
Thank you, Mao.

22:58.300 --> 23:00.619
Thank you for talking to me so much.

23:02.260 --> 23:03.260
It's been a long time

23:04.340 --> 23:05.500
since I've been this happy.

23:06.340 --> 23:08.740
If you have any problems in the future, just tell me.

23:10.459 --> 23:11.939
Don't keep it all inside.

23:13.379 --> 23:14.020
It's exhausting.

23:18.459 --> 23:19.260
Honestly,

23:20.899 --> 23:22.300
I've always been hesitant

23:23.300 --> 23:24.100
to talk about

23:24.100 --> 23:25.139
my family with others.

23:28.139 --> 23:28.980
It feels like

23:30.100 --> 23:31.740
I'm constantly reopening

23:32.619 --> 23:34.980
my wounds

23:34.980 --> 23:36.619
just to get sympathy.

23:40.100 --> 23:41.219
But I don't want to hide anything from you.

23:43.580 --> 23:45.139
Relationships are about two families,

23:46.619 --> 23:49.100
but marriage is about two families.

23:52.060 --> 23:52.820
Although we

23:52.820 --> 23:54.060
haven't gotten to that point yet,

23:56.699 --> 23:57.580
before,

23:58.540 --> 24:00.060
when the people I went on blind dates with

24:00.060 --> 24:01.500
found out about my family situation,

24:02.619 --> 24:04.260
they all backed out.

24:07.219 --> 24:08.340
I've already thought about

24:08.899 --> 24:09.899
being alone until I die.

24:10.419 --> 24:11.060
Shanshan,

24:11.859 --> 24:13.179
don't ever think like that.

24:13.659 --> 24:14.619
A girl as good as you

24:14.619 --> 24:15.939
how could you end up alone?

24:20.659 --> 24:21.980
It's not your fault.

24:22.659 --> 24:23.859
You've been through a lot.

24:24.899 --> 24:25.619
Don't worry.

24:25.619 --> 24:26.740
I don't care about your background,

24:26.740 --> 24:27.980
or your family.

24:28.780 --> 24:29.340
Right?

24:37.980 --> 24:38.580
We're out of wine.

24:38.780 --> 24:39.260
Waiter.

24:39.659 --> 24:40.139
Yes, sir?

24:40.139 --> 24:40.980
Another bottle, please.

24:41.379 --> 24:41.859
Okay.

24:47.500 --> 24:48.100
Lawyer Xu.

24:51.820 --> 24:52.300
I'll take it.

24:52.580 --> 24:53.859
Thank you.

24:54.859 --> 24:55.379
Okay.

25:01.740 --> 25:02.219
Thanks.

25:07.179 --> 25:07.820
I'll take this call.

25:10.340 --> 25:10.780
Hello?

25:14.939 --> 25:15.859
Send me the address.

25:16.020 --> 25:16.820
I'll be there soon.

25:18.419 --> 25:18.859
Okay.

25:20.939 --> 25:21.780
What happened?

25:26.619 --> 25:27.459
Don't worry.

25:27.939 --> 25:29.139
I'm definitely not a scammer.

25:29.419 --> 25:29.980
It's okay, it's okay.

25:31.659 --> 25:33.100
My friend will be here soon.

25:33.100 --> 25:34.219
He'll take care of this order.

25:34.540 --> 25:35.020
Okay.

25:40.980 --> 25:41.699
Why are your prices

25:41.699 --> 25:42.699
so high at this restaurant?

25:43.540 --> 25:44.060
Well,

25:44.540 --> 25:45.899
you just opened three bottles

25:45.899 --> 25:47.219
of 2015 Harlan.

25:47.619 --> 25:49.980
The price per bottle is 25,999.

25:50.419 --> 25:52.300
25,999 per bottle?

25:52.659 --> 25:53.179
Yes.

25:55.659 --> 25:57.219
Why isn't it on the menu?

25:57.659 --> 25:58.139
No.

25:58.780 --> 26:00.060
Everything in our restaurant

26:00.060 --> 26:01.260
is

26:02.459 --> 26:03.260
clearly priced.

26:07.179 --> 26:08.379
What's wrong, Mao?

26:08.899 --> 26:09.540
Nothing.

26:10.260 --> 26:10.859
Shanshan,

26:12.659 --> 26:13.820
where's my card?

26:13.980 --> 26:14.859
It's over the limit.

26:15.260 --> 26:16.139
Don't worry.

26:16.379 --> 26:17.459
I called my friend.

26:17.459 --> 26:18.419
He'll be here soon

26:18.419 --> 26:19.419
and take care of this.

26:19.899 --> 26:20.780
I can pay.

26:21.020 --> 26:21.899
No, no, no.

26:22.899 --> 26:24.300
How could I let you pay?

26:25.379 --> 26:25.899
Listen to me.

26:26.060 --> 26:27.100
Just go back and wait.

26:27.300 --> 26:28.500
It'll be done soon.

27:01.139 --> 27:01.899
Are you still sober?

27:03.379 --> 27:04.179
Song.

27:05.699 --> 27:06.699
You're here.

27:09.820 --> 27:10.580
Drink some water

27:11.100 --> 27:11.740
and sober up.

27:16.300 --> 27:17.060
Are you here

27:17.300 --> 27:18.419
to pay the bill for your friend?

27:19.740 --> 27:20.100
Yes.

27:21.179 --> 27:22.540
May I see the receipt?

27:24.580 --> 27:25.500
Thank you.

27:34.100 --> 27:34.580
Do you know her?

27:35.100 --> 27:35.619
No.

27:36.939 --> 27:37.340
Okay.

27:45.459 --> 27:46.340
Song,

27:47.659 --> 27:49.179
let me introduce.

27:50.500 --> 27:51.899
This is Shanshan.

27:52.820 --> 27:53.419
Shanshan,

27:54.100 --> 27:55.939
this is my best friend,

27:56.379 --> 27:58.939
Xu Huaisong, Lawyer Xu.

28:01.100 --> 28:01.980
Lawyer Xu, nice to meet you.

28:02.340 --> 28:03.699
Brother Mao often talks about you.

28:03.740 --> 28:05.060
He says you're really good at handling cases.

28:06.980 --> 28:07.899
So, you're Shanshan?

28:08.459 --> 28:08.820
Have a seat.

28:12.419 --> 28:13.619
I need to tell you something.

28:14.500 --> 28:16.100
Do you know that based on your current actions,

28:16.419 --> 28:17.300
you could be suspected

28:17.300 --> 28:18.820
as a criminal offense?

28:21.300 --> 28:23.300
What do you mean?

28:23.300 --> 28:24.740
I don't understand.

28:25.060 --> 28:26.859
Don't be frightened by him.

28:27.060 --> 28:28.340
He's kidding.

28:28.340 --> 28:29.939
He likes to make fun.

28:31.179 --> 28:31.939
It's his occupational disease.

28:31.939 --> 28:33.659
He wants to sue anyone he meets.

28:35.419 --> 28:36.260
You drank fake wine,

28:36.260 --> 28:37.060
and you don't even know

28:37.060 --> 28:37.859
you were cheated.

28:37.859 --> 28:38.780
What fake wine?

28:39.740 --> 28:40.540
You didn't drink.

28:40.540 --> 28:41.899
Why are you talking nonsense?

28:42.340 --> 28:43.139
A bottle of ordinary wine

28:43.139 --> 28:44.619
costing 300 or 500 yuan.

28:45.060 --> 28:46.699
With a label and repackaging,

28:47.020 --> 28:48.139
it sells for 26,000 yuan.

28:48.500 --> 28:49.379
How much commission?

28:50.659 --> 28:51.219
I'm not asking you.

28:56.939 --> 28:57.740
Lawyer Xu,

28:58.500 --> 29:00.020
we've just met today.

29:00.939 --> 29:02.260
I don't understand why

29:02.260 --> 29:03.419
you're so malicious towards me.

29:03.419 --> 29:05.980
But I'm really into Mao.

29:06.260 --> 29:07.820
She's really nice.

29:08.780 --> 29:09.379
Really?

29:10.619 --> 29:11.260
For the sake of Liu Mao

29:11.260 --> 29:12.580
being really into you,

29:12.939 --> 29:13.740
I'll give you

29:13.740 --> 29:15.340
some free advice as a lawyer.

29:16.139 --> 29:17.139
Intentionally producing

29:17.139 --> 29:18.260
and selling inferior products.

29:18.659 --> 29:19.939
The bill today

29:20.219 --> 29:21.300
is enough to convict you.

29:24.139 --> 29:25.060
What evidence do you have?

29:25.780 --> 29:26.820
The wine is physical evidence.

29:27.619 --> 29:28.780
The transaction records

29:28.780 --> 29:29.659
between you and the restaurant manager

29:29.980 --> 29:30.659
are documentary evidence.

29:36.500 --> 29:37.740
I don't know what you're talking about.

29:37.740 --> 29:38.419
Lawyer Xu.

29:39.219 --> 29:40.179
I don't know

29:40.179 --> 29:41.060
the manager at all.

29:41.580 --> 29:42.939
And if there's a problem with the wine,

29:42.939 --> 29:43.980
it's the restaurant's fault.

29:45.179 --> 29:46.379
I'm also a victim.

29:46.740 --> 29:47.580
Yeah.

29:48.300 --> 29:48.939
Then I...

29:49.419 --> 29:51.179
We are all victims.

29:51.179 --> 29:52.619
You are a victim, but she's not.

29:53.179 --> 29:54.540
I just checked the wine glass.

29:55.379 --> 29:56.260
If you drank it,

29:56.260 --> 29:57.219
you are a victim.

29:57.740 --> 29:59.219
How can you talk to me

29:59.219 --> 30:00.060
so clearly?

30:00.859 --> 30:01.540
Besides,

30:02.740 --> 30:03.780
the water stain below...

30:06.500 --> 30:07.179
Shanshan,

30:08.459 --> 30:10.139
I'm a bit confused now.

30:10.139 --> 30:10.980
I heard

30:12.100 --> 30:13.659
he said about the wine glass

30:13.659 --> 30:14.859
and

30:14.859 --> 30:16.580
the water stain on the ground.

30:16.580 --> 30:17.459
What does it mean?

30:18.260 --> 30:19.379
Mao, I didn't.

30:20.100 --> 30:20.540
I...

30:21.500 --> 30:22.260
Tell me the truth.

30:26.100 --> 30:27.340
Did you lie to me?

30:28.980 --> 30:29.740
I'm sorry. I...

30:31.100 --> 30:31.859
You are a good person.

30:34.780 --> 30:37.459
Shanshan, where are you going?

30:39.699 --> 30:40.139
Go.

30:40.939 --> 30:41.459
Wait.

30:44.899 --> 30:45.300
I've been

30:45.300 --> 30:46.580
listening to you for a long time.

30:47.300 --> 30:48.219
Don't think you can fool me

30:48.219 --> 30:49.100
by saying that.

30:49.659 --> 30:50.500
I'm telling you,

30:50.820 --> 30:51.659
no one can leave

30:52.219 --> 30:53.060
until the bill is settled.

30:54.580 --> 30:55.139
Sit for a while.

30:57.780 --> 30:59.100
Then don't go.

31:00.139 --> 31:00.820
Passing off fake as real

31:00.820 --> 31:01.939
is already a violation of the Criminal Law,

31:01.939 --> 31:02.899
Article 140.

31:03.459 --> 31:04.419
Wine fraud,

31:04.540 --> 31:05.580
intimidating consumers.

31:06.540 --> 31:08.060
Every word you just said

31:08.659 --> 31:09.619
has been recorded.

31:10.540 --> 31:11.659
Recording is not allowed in our restaurant.

31:11.980 --> 31:12.939
You are infringing on our privacy.

31:13.980 --> 31:14.219
You...

31:14.419 --> 31:15.419
If you want it, just take it.

31:16.020 --> 31:17.060
All the recordings

31:17.060 --> 31:18.980
have been uploaded to the cloud storage.

31:19.939 --> 31:21.060
And I know better than you

31:21.419 --> 31:22.500
that legal evidence collection

31:22.780 --> 31:23.740
is still an infringement of privacy.

31:23.939 --> 31:24.540
One more thing.

31:25.060 --> 31:26.340
I've already called the police.

31:27.060 --> 31:27.899
They'll be here

31:27.899 --> 31:28.859
in a few minutes.

31:29.060 --> 31:30.340
If you have anything to say,

31:30.859 --> 31:32.020
just tell them.

31:32.300 --> 31:32.659
You...

31:37.699 --> 31:39.060
When did you call the police?

31:41.859 --> 31:42.459
Just now,

31:44.260 --> 31:44.859
before getting in the car.

31:45.740 --> 31:48.780
You are indeed a cunning old fox.

31:56.100 --> 31:56.619
Are you okay?

31:59.060 --> 32:00.100
I'm fine.

32:03.619 --> 32:06.500
Since ancient times, heroes have always fallen for beauties.

32:07.980 --> 32:10.419
This time, you have definitely

32:10.419 --> 32:11.939
taken a different path

32:11.939 --> 32:13.740
and become a hero.

32:15.179 --> 32:15.980
You can still joke around.

32:16.580 --> 32:17.419
It seems that there is no problem.

32:17.820 --> 32:18.300
I'm fine.

32:19.740 --> 32:20.780
I'm just a little hungry.

32:21.340 --> 32:22.500
The whole meal

32:22.699 --> 32:23.699
was eaten by that girl.

32:26.939 --> 32:28.060
Shanshan said she was hungry,

32:28.060 --> 32:29.459
so I gave her all my steak.

32:29.459 --> 32:30.899
I was too busy drinking.

32:33.780 --> 32:34.659
Did you eat anything?

32:34.859 --> 32:36.020
You're really not helping.

32:36.340 --> 32:37.419
If you were ten minutes later,

32:37.419 --> 32:38.419
I would have eaten.

32:40.419 --> 32:42.540
Then let me treat you to something.

32:45.139 --> 32:45.740
After the police come

32:45.740 --> 32:46.459
and finish the record,

32:46.939 --> 32:47.659
let's grab a late-night snack.

32:48.859 --> 32:49.340
Sure,

32:51.740 --> 32:53.300
but let's find a cheaper place this time.

33:11.659 --> 33:12.619
Song,

33:15.859 --> 33:17.419
I've had enough heartbreak.

33:19.459 --> 33:20.340
Why is dating

33:21.580 --> 33:22.659
so hard?

33:28.060 --> 33:28.659
It's not heartbreak

33:28.659 --> 33:29.820
you're dealing with,

33:30.300 --> 33:31.300
it's being conned.

33:31.740 --> 33:33.300
As a lawyer,

33:33.659 --> 33:35.060
you got tricked by a bar scammer.

33:35.379 --> 33:36.619
Don't tell people tomorrow

33:36.619 --> 33:37.699
that you are a partner of Zhikun.

33:40.139 --> 33:40.939
What's wrong with a lawyer?

33:41.780 --> 33:43.060
Don't lawyers have feelings?

33:44.899 --> 33:46.020
You said she was a scammer.

33:46.580 --> 33:47.699
To trick me,

33:48.379 --> 33:50.060
she made up such a story.

33:50.859 --> 33:51.699
From

33:52.500 --> 33:54.060
another perspective,

33:55.219 --> 33:56.020
doesn't that mean

33:56.020 --> 33:57.100
she likes me a bit?

33:57.659 --> 33:58.780
She put a lot of effort into it.

33:59.500 --> 34:01.340
You're still not getting the message.

34:09.379 --> 34:10.580
So, I'm just

34:11.500 --> 34:13.340
a cog in the wheel?

34:14.939 --> 34:16.020
At this point,

34:16.259 --> 34:16.980
just let it go.

34:28.940 --> 34:30.299
If she doesn't like me,

34:31.179 --> 34:32.339
why would she chat with me

34:32.339 --> 34:33.339
when I'm feeling down?

34:33.580 --> 34:34.540
Wasn't that you

34:34.540 --> 34:35.580
texting her first?

34:35.819 --> 34:36.860
And when I said I wanted something sweet,

34:37.460 --> 34:38.540
she made it for me herself!

34:38.580 --> 34:39.299
But you were the one

34:39.299 --> 34:40.380
who said you wanted it.

34:45.380 --> 34:46.659
So all this sweetness

34:46.659 --> 34:47.779
was just me asking for it?

34:48.259 --> 34:49.339
It's all just one-sided?

34:49.699 --> 34:50.860
What's wrong with asking?

34:52.259 --> 34:53.060
Just because you asked for candy

34:53.060 --> 34:54.139
doesn't mean it's not candy.

34:55.179 --> 34:55.980
Just because you asked for candy

34:56.100 --> 34:56.940
doesn't mean it's not sweet.

34:58.179 --> 34:58.980
It's candy.

34:59.819 --> 35:00.819
Just eat it.

35:03.819 --> 35:05.739
Since you enjoyed the process,

35:05.980 --> 35:07.779
don't care about the result.

35:08.139 --> 35:09.060
I worked so hard

35:09.060 --> 35:10.060
to maintain the process.

35:10.060 --> 35:11.219
Isn't it because I want a

35:11.219 --> 35:12.259
good result?

35:14.619 --> 35:15.299
When they were talking about me,

35:15.299 --> 35:16.500
you were pretty cool.

35:17.580 --> 35:18.819
When you heard that

35:18.819 --> 35:19.739
the novel ended,

35:19.739 --> 35:20.139
didn't you

35:20.139 --> 35:21.060
feel bad for two days?

35:48.900 --> 35:50.259
[Next week is New Year's Eve.]

35:50.540 --> 35:52.380
[Students who want to exchange gifts,]

35:52.380 --> 35:53.659
[please hand them over to the Culture and Entertainment Department.]

35:54.139 --> 35:55.299
[The department will organize a drawing of lots]

35:55.299 --> 35:56.779
[the day before New Year's Eve.]

36:32.779 --> 36:33.819
Don't even think about it.

36:34.380 --> 36:35.659
The kids are still so young.

36:35.659 --> 36:36.900
How can they go to America with you?

36:37.940 --> 36:39.580
I'm discussing this with you, aren't I?

36:40.580 --> 36:41.779
You should at least ask

36:41.779 --> 36:42.699
the kids' opinion.

36:43.100 --> 36:43.940
No need to ask.

36:44.460 --> 36:45.779
Huai Shi won't go with you.

38:45.179 --> 38:46.020
Brother.

38:50.980 --> 38:52.060
Brother.

38:54.100 --> 38:57.580
Mom and Dad are going to...

38:58.299 --> 38:59.940
Going to divorce.

39:01.860 --> 39:02.540
I know.

39:03.339 --> 39:04.619
Don't cry. Don't cry.

39:06.580 --> 39:07.860
Let's go back to our room, okay?

39:29.100 --> 39:30.020
Brother.

39:30.460 --> 39:32.580
From now on,

39:33.339 --> 39:34.619
can we only

39:34.619 --> 39:36.619
have one of them?

39:38.619 --> 39:42.339
Mom said Dad was going to America.

39:43.060 --> 39:45.420
She asked me if I wanted to go.

39:50.380 --> 39:53.500
I don't want to go that far away.

39:54.380 --> 39:57.500
I don't know anyone there.

39:58.659 --> 40:02.900
I don't want to go with Dad.

40:27.900 --> 40:29.420
I won't let you go to America.

40:31.179 --> 40:32.339
Really?

40:41.219 --> 40:41.860
Really.

40:43.179 --> 40:43.699
Don't cry.

41:04.699 --> 41:05.380
Brother.

41:06.139 --> 41:07.339
What's that?

41:26.420 --> 41:27.460
It's a gift.

41:52.980 --> 41:53.460
for you.

42:05.580 --> 42:07.060
[If I hadn't backed down,]

42:08.420 --> 42:09.580
[would the outcome have been different?]

42:36.940 --> 42:39.299
Brother, will Sister Ruan Yu's case

42:39.299 --> 42:40.900
go to court tomorrow?

42:43.179 --> 42:44.339
I'll go and cheer her up,

42:44.500 --> 42:45.060
and give her some support.

42:45.779 --> 42:47.060
The trial is about to start.

42:47.420 --> 42:48.980
How are things going with Ruan Yu?

42:49.860 --> 42:50.619
It's going well.

42:50.900 --> 42:51.540
Don't worry about it.

42:54.339 --> 42:55.420
When I asked you yesterday,

42:55.420 --> 42:56.339
you were still upset.

42:56.819 --> 42:58.139
You've figured it out today?

42:58.699 --> 43:00.380
The novel's ending was her idea before.

43:00.699 --> 43:01.500
It doesn't mean the present,

43:01.940 --> 43:02.860
let alone the future.

43:06.139 --> 43:07.980
One night's reflection, and you're a different person.

43:08.619 --> 43:09.380
Impressive.

43:09.819 --> 43:11.139
The sky's cleared, the rain's stopped,

43:11.500 --> 43:12.380
and my brother's back on track.

43:13.860 --> 43:14.460
What about you?

43:15.060 --> 43:15.619
Your homeroom teacher

43:15.619 --> 43:16.860
sent me your last month's

43:16.860 --> 43:17.500
your monthly exam results.

43:18.060 --> 43:19.420
They don't look good.

43:21.500 --> 43:22.779
I'm busy. Bye.

43:38.139 --> 43:39.060
Another post

43:39.619 --> 43:41.139
from Sister Ruan Yu.

43:46.739 --> 43:47.739
Giving it my all

43:47.739 --> 43:48.980
and trying without regrets

43:49.380 --> 43:51.179
is a kind of fulfillment.

43:52.460 --> 43:53.339
You've got

43:53.339 --> 43:55.179
a point, Song.

43:57.020 --> 43:59.819
Backing down means regrets.

44:01.020 --> 44:03.420
But if we fight for it,

44:05.259 --> 44:06.460
we'll be able to

44:06.460 --> 44:08.100
justify our feelings.

44:10.100 --> 44:11.420
It's like a lawsuit.

44:12.020 --> 44:13.699
No matter the outcome,

44:15.100 --> 44:16.860
just do it.

44:36.540 --> 44:38.380
Xu Huaisong actually likes posts?

44:39.259 --> 44:40.900
Never seen him like Liu Mao's.

44:41.819 --> 44:42.420
So

44:42.619 --> 44:43.860
he does browse WeChat Moments?

45:02.460 --> 45:03.980
[I'll pick you up at 7 a.m. tomorrow.]

45:08.299 --> 45:09.299
This must be

45:10.179 --> 45:11.619
the last time we meet, right?

45:17.420 --> 45:18.739
Since the defendant

45:18.940 --> 45:19.819
didn't show up,

45:20.739 --> 45:22.860
and the plaintiff

45:23.460 --> 45:24.819
refused mediation,

45:25.779 --> 45:27.540
we'll postpone the ruling.

45:28.299 --> 45:30.500
The decision will be mailed

45:30.500 --> 45:31.219
to both parties.

45:31.779 --> 45:32.619
Court adjourned.

45:36.060 --> 45:36.580
Ms. Cen,

45:37.179 --> 45:38.299
I did my best.

45:38.900 --> 45:40.380
The plaintiff insisted on not mediating.

45:40.980 --> 45:42.259
Based on today's hearing,

45:42.860 --> 45:43.699
the court is likely to

45:43.699 --> 45:44.699
support her claim.

45:46.299 --> 45:46.900
Okay.

45:49.259 --> 45:49.860
I see.

46:19.540 --> 46:20.900
It should be fine, right, Lawyer Xu?

46:21.500 --> 46:22.139
Don't worry.

46:22.460 --> 46:23.540
If all goes well, you'll receive

46:23.540 --> 46:24.420
the judgment within a month.

46:24.980 --> 46:26.100
Once it's published online,

46:26.339 --> 46:27.060
this matter

46:27.179 --> 46:28.259
will be completely resolved.

46:29.500 --> 46:30.100
That's good.

46:30.860 --> 46:31.580
Sorry

46:31.580 --> 46:32.139
to keep you waiting.

46:32.380 --> 46:33.339
My old problem.

46:33.540 --> 46:34.540
I always have diarrhea

46:34.779 --> 46:35.619
after court.

46:36.900 --> 46:38.699
I need to practice my mentality.

46:39.619 --> 46:40.460
All right, let's go.

46:40.779 --> 46:41.819
The enemy has been defeated.

46:41.819 --> 46:43.339
We can go back

46:43.580 --> 46:44.420
and rest.

46:44.900 --> 46:45.219
Let's go.

46:45.219 --> 46:45.699
Go.

46:52.139 --> 46:52.860
Hello, Mingying.

46:52.860 --> 46:53.659
Check Weibo.

46:54.659 --> 46:55.699
Cen Sisi committed suicide.

46:55.699 --> 46:56.619
Many netizens are guessing

46:56.619 --> 46:57.699
that you forced her to do it.

47:02.100 --> 47:02.580
What's wrong?

47:07.980 --> 47:08.819
Cen Sisi

47:09.940 --> 47:10.619
committed suicide.

47:33.779 --> 47:35.219
One fried dough stick, two eggs,

47:35.819 --> 47:36.420
and a cup of soy milk.

47:38.500 --> 47:39.739
The fried dough stick should be soft.

47:39.980 --> 47:41.219
Fried dough stick and eggs are the best.

47:41.420 --> 47:42.779
Lawyer Xu, you also believe in this?

47:44.540 --> 47:45.139
Boss,

47:45.259 --> 47:46.540
I want a dough stick and two eggs.

47:48.659 --> 47:49.659
In junior high,

47:49.659 --> 47:50.460
a dough stick and two eggs

47:50.540 --> 47:51.659
can get 100 points.

47:51.659 --> 47:52.580
Now in senior high,

47:52.580 --> 47:53.699
Chinese, math, and English are all 150 points.

47:54.100 --> 47:55.540
Aren't politics, history, and geography still 100 points?

47:56.020 --> 47:56.659
Besides,

47:56.900 --> 47:57.739
my 100

47:57.739 --> 47:59.179
also means 100 percent.

47:59.500 --> 48:00.819
I'm sending a signal

48:00.819 --> 48:01.580
to my brain

48:01.900 --> 48:02.980
to give it more energy

48:02.980 --> 48:04.420
and intelligence to face the exam.

48:05.420 --> 48:05.900
Do you understand?

48:06.739 --> 48:07.219
Give me money.

48:07.219 --> 48:08.299
More intelligence.

48:10.900 --> 48:11.819
I used to believe this,

48:11.819 --> 48:12.819
and I was even laughed at.

48:13.380 --> 48:14.940
Boss, I want one too.

48:15.580 --> 48:16.380
This one is for you.

48:18.139 --> 48:19.699
Lawyer Xu, don't you eat it yourself?

48:20.900 --> 48:21.819
My breakfast hasn't arrived yet.

48:22.940 --> 48:24.020
Thank you. One more douhua,

48:24.060 --> 48:24.659
and an egg.

48:24.779 --> 48:25.219
How much?

48:27.020 --> 48:27.420
25 yuan.

48:27.739 --> 48:28.339
Okay, thank you.

48:31.980 --> 48:32.819
Morning, Ruan Yu, Lawyer Liu.

48:33.980 --> 48:34.339
Okay.

48:34.339 --> 48:35.219
I've paid for the breakfast.

48:35.980 --> 48:36.380
Have a seat.

48:37.420 --> 48:38.219
Come on.

48:40.060 --> 48:41.219
This is for you. It's good for your brain.

48:45.739 --> 48:46.699
And yours.

48:54.299 --> 48:54.940
By the way,

48:55.460 --> 48:56.819
can you show me

48:56.980 --> 48:57.819
the trial materials again?

48:58.259 --> 48:59.619
I want to review them

49:00.060 --> 49:00.779
to feel more prepared.

49:01.139 --> 49:02.060
Sure.

49:02.980 --> 49:03.779
It's in my bag.

49:04.179 --> 49:04.500
Okay.

49:10.500 --> 49:11.259
Not that one.

49:11.819 --> 49:12.500
That's the other side's.

49:14.219 --> 49:15.299
It's just the tip of the iceberg.

49:15.580 --> 49:16.659
can you tell the difference?

49:17.299 --> 49:17.779
Is it because they

49:17.779 --> 49:18.819
have different thickness?

49:19.420 --> 49:20.299
Because that clip

49:21.980 --> 49:22.619
is yellow.

49:26.980 --> 49:28.980
So, this green clip

49:28.980 --> 49:30.259
is for our own file,

49:30.420 --> 49:32.139
which means green light all the way.

49:32.900 --> 49:33.380
Smart.

49:35.339 --> 49:36.860
Do lawyers believe in these things?

49:38.339 --> 49:39.659
Or is it because my case

49:39.659 --> 49:40.380
is rather complicated,

49:40.380 --> 49:41.420
So it needs

49:41.420 --> 49:42.060
more luck.

49:42.580 --> 49:43.580
This case

49:43.980 --> 49:45.339
is indeed a small one.

49:45.739 --> 49:46.500
But

49:47.659 --> 49:49.100
we have a lawyer

49:49.100 --> 49:50.739
who always fulfills the wishes

49:50.739 --> 49:51.619
of her clients.

49:52.100 --> 49:53.420
I saw your post on WeChat yesterday.

49:54.100 --> 49:55.980
You wanted a lucky charm.

49:56.500 --> 49:57.739
So here you are.

50:00.420 --> 50:01.699
Did you sleep well last night?

50:04.100 --> 50:04.980
It's your first lawsuit,

50:05.500 --> 50:06.739
so you must be a little nervous, right?

50:09.219 --> 50:09.940
But

50:10.139 --> 50:11.580
I have two great lawyers backing me up.

50:11.940 --> 50:12.699
Even the file holders

50:12.699 --> 50:13.940
are taken care of.

50:15.139 --> 50:15.980
I feel very reassured.

50:16.420 --> 50:17.259
I slept very well last night.

50:18.860 --> 50:19.619
With this mindset,

50:19.739 --> 50:20.540
our case

50:21.179 --> 50:21.659
is bound to win.
